Home Furniture and Lighting Products
Home Furniture and Lighting Products include sofas, bed frames, mattresses, customized furniture, and intelligent lighting systems eligible for subsidies under the program.

Jinan
Jinan is the city where the 2025 Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program is implemented.

Sanitary Ware Products
Sanitary Ware Products include smart toilets, bathroom cabinets, and bathtubs eligible for subsidies under the program.

Personal Consumers
Personal consumers are the target participants of the 2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program, limited to homeowners within Jinan city.

Smart Home Products
Smart Home Products include smart locks, intelligent laundry racks, gateways, routers, and smart sockets eligible for subsidies under the program.

Construction Bank Life App
The Construction Bank Life App is a mobile application used by consumers to register, upload property information, claim subsidy vouchers, and process discounts during the program.

data.entity_name: 2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program
data.content:
2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program
The 2025 Jinan Home Renovation and Furniture Subsidy Program is a municipal initiative aimed at providing financial support for home improvement and furniture purchases through various subsidies.

Home Renovation Materials
Home Renovation Materials include items like doors, windows, wood flooring, tiles, paint, wallpaper, shower rooms, and partitions eligible for subsidies under the program.

Senior-Friendly Home Modification
Senior-Friendly Home Modification is a category of subsidy designed for making homes more suitable for elderly living that is implemented by the civil affairs departments but detailed rules will be announced later.

Smart Toilet Efficiency Standards
The Smart Toilet Efficiency Standards refer to a regulatory benchmark that specifies water and energy usage levels for smart toilet products eligible for a higher subsidy rate.

建行生活-济南
建行生活-济南is the official WeChat account providing information and services related to the济南家装补贴campaign.

消费补贴券
消费补贴券are discount coupons issued for the济南家装补贴initiative, featuring specific usage rules and limitations.

Civil Affairs Department of Jinan
The Civil Affairs Department of Jinan is responsible for implementing the guidelines and rules related to Senior-Friendly Home Modification under the program.

Discounted Sales Prices
Discounted Sales Prices refer to the actual prices of eligible products after discounts, which form the basis for the subsidy calculation under the program.

泉惠企
泉惠企is a service platform used by merchants for submitting subsidy applications within the济南家装补贴campaign.

Notarization Documents and Property Certificates
Notarization Documents and Property Certificates are official documents required to verify homeownership for participation in the subsidy program.

山东省装饰协会
山东省装饰协会reviews and approves product lists for the subsidy activities in the济南家装补贴campaign.

家装补贴
家装补贴refers to a subsidy initiative aimed at promoting home renovation and refurbishment in济南.

建行生活APP
建行生活APP is an application used by consumers for redeeming discount coupons and making payments under the subsidy initiative.

济南市商务局
济南市商务局is the governing body overseeing the subsidy initiative, holding the right to the final interpretation of the rules.

data.entity_name: 2025年济南市家装、家居焕新补贴活动
data.content:
2025年济南市家装、家居焕新补贴活动
2025年济南市家装、家居“焕新”补贴活动is a subsidy event organized by济南市商务局to incentivize home improvement and furnishing.

Property Registration System of Jinan
The Property Registration System of Jinan is an official system used to verify the status and ownership of real estate within the city for the subsidy program.

政策服务
政策服务is a portal on the泉惠企platform for merchants to access guidance on policy-related matters.

消费者详细流程
消费者详细流程provides detailed guidelines for consumers on how to participate in the subsidy initiative via建行生活-济南.

商家详细流程
商家详细流程provides step-by-step instructions for merchants applying for subsidies under the济南家装补贴campaign.

家居类补贴
家居类补贴refers to the category-specific discounts offered for furniture, smart home equipment, and homegoods under the subsidy initiative.

工作日咨询热线
工作日咨询热线are phone numbers provided for consumer and merchant inquiries regarding the subsidy activities.

家装类补贴
家装类补贴refers to the category-specific discounts offered for renovation materials and related products under the subsidy initiative.
